      <title>金正恩直言不讳的妹妹猛烈抨击美国针对贸易而出口武器的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/kim-jong-un-s-outspoken-sister-blasts-claims-of-arms-exports-as-us-targets-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国对武器贸易实施新制裁后不久，朝鲜领导人直言不讳的妹妹就指责朝鲜向俄罗斯出口武器的指控是“虚构的”。华盛顿称，武器贸易为克里姆林宫袭击乌克兰提供了动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/kim-jong-un-s-outspoken-sister-blasts-claims-of-arms-exports-as-us-targets-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:11:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界银行寻求外部调查员调查肯尼亚的虐待指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/world-bank-seeks-outside-investigator-to-look-into-inquiry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行周四表示，将寻求“一家外部公司”来调查该行监察员在肯尼亚学校性虐待指控调查方面的工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/world-bank-seeks-outside-investigator-to-look-into-inquiry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 00:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
